{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/noahbuscher/inspire/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1c2f2879-bf38-5aa9-b20a-eab6ad0cec95","html":"<h1 id=\"inspire-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inspire-awesome\" aria-label=\"inspire awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Inspire <a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>Designing and building a modern frontend in any web project can be a long and arduous process. Here's a collection of links to help you. Enjoy!</p>\n<h2 id=\"concept\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#concept\" aria-label=\"concept permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Concept</h2>\n<h5>These sites are good to get a general idea of possible layouts and style paths to take.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thebestdesigns.com/\">TheBestDesigns</a> - General list of hand picked sites from across the web.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.awwwards.com/\">Awwwards</a> - More awesome sites of various styles.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://dribbble.com/\">Dribbble</a> - Snaps of icons, doodles, sites, and more from a talented group of people.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siiimple.com/\">Siiimple</a> - Another list of sites, but on the much simpler side.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://httpster.net/\">Httpster</a> - A curated list of the best sites around the Internet.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://saaspages.xyz\">SaaS Pages</a> - An inspection of Netlify's page made especially to bring you inspiration.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.siteinspire.com/\">siteInspire</a> - Get inspired.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.designernews.co/\">Designer News</a> - The best design / development links from the 'net.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.csswinner.com/\">CSS Winner</a> - Reviewed list of great websites.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://onepagelove.com/\">OnePageLove</a> - Great influence for one page and general website design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codemyui.com/\">CodeMyUI</a> - List of code snippets for fancy CSS/JS that make an awesome UI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://codepen.io/\">CodePen</a> - Central repository of user submitted code concepts/snippets. Great for experiments.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://codyhouse.co/\">CodyHouse</a> - Tutorials and showcase of awesome UI elements.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.justinaguilar.com/animations/#\">CSS3 Cheat Sheet</a> - CSS3 Cheat Sheet</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"creation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#creation\" aria-label=\"creation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creation</h2>\n<h5>These sites are good for building a basic framework for the site.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Color\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://colorswall.com/\">ColorsWall</a> - Place to store your color palettes.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://coolors.co/\">Coolors</a> - Super fast color scheme generator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://color.adobe.com/\">Kuler</a> - Easily create or view a custom color swatch for your site.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://uigradients.com/\">uiGradients</a> - Gorgous gradient generator.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://jxnblk.com/Spectral/\">Spectral</a> - Minimal color swatch creation.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://unsemantic.com\">Unsemantic</a> - Provides a good grid framework for small to large projects.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org\">MDN</a> - Documentation for HTML, CSS, JS, etc.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://getbootstrap.com\">Bootstrap</a> - Very popular framework for building modern websites and web apps.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://bootswatch.com\">Bootswatch</a> - A list of free themes for Bootstrap.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://iconscout.com\">iconscout.com</a> - Get high-quality Icons, Illustrations and Stock photos at one place.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://iconmonstr.com\">Iconmonstr</a> - A collection of free, simple icons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://ionicons.com\">Ionicons</a> - Another great collection of free icons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://subtlepatterns.com\">Subtle Patterns</a> - A massive archive of free backgrounds for your projects.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.google.com/fonts\">Google Fonts</a> - Tons of free, easy to use webfonts.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://patorjk.com/software/taag/#p=display&#x26;f=Graffiti&#x26;t=Type%20Something%20\">Text to ASCII</a> - Add some sexy Easter eggs in your source code.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.justinaguilar.com/animations/\">CSS3 Animation Cheat Sheet</a> - A collection of CSS3 animation snippets.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://designmodo.github.io/Flat-UI/\">Flat UI</a> - A superb HTML and CSS framework for flat design. It's the juice.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://css2stylus.com\">CSS2Stylus</a> - Convert your CSS to Stylus.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://youmightnotneedjquery.com\">YMNNJQ</a> - See jQuery functions in natural JS. No libraries.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://uifaces.com\">User Inter Faces</a> - Get ipsum images for user images.</li>\n<li>Images\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://allthefreestock.com/\">AllTheFreeStock</a> - All the Free stock mmages, videos, sounds and icons in one location.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://thestocks.im\">TheStocks.im</a> - A collection of great stock photo websites.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://unsplash.com\">Unsplash</a> - Free, high quality stock photos.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://minwiz.com/\">MinWiz</a> - Starter kit for minimal, viable, good looking, production-ready websites.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h2>\n<h5>Every painter needs a brush. Well... Most do.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sublimetext.com\">Sublime Text</a> - A very popular text editor for developers.\n<ul>\n<li>Themes\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/noahbuscher/Flatron\">Flatron</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/noahbuscher/Flatron\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">249</span></span></a> - It's flat, purple, and hella sexy.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jamiewilson/predawn\">Predawn</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jamiewilson/predawn\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.8k</span></span></a> - Gorgeous dark interface and syntax theme.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://atom.io\">Atom</a> - A hackable text editor for the 21st century.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://brackets.io/\">Brackets</a> - Modern, open source editor with live preview.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\">VSCode</a> - Free text editor</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hyper.is\">Hyper</a> - Beautiful, extensible command-line interface</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://filezilla-project.org\">FileZilla</a> - For those who fear FTP in the terminal.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://winscp.net\">WinSCP</a> - Upload files to a MEAN stack or VPS server.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.sketchapp.com/\">Sketch</a> [OS X only] - A professional vector graphics app.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.taskade.com/\">Taskade</a> [OS X only] - Create beautiful task lists and outlines.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://devsession.js.org/\">DevSession</a> - Open a collaborative online IDE from a local directory.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"collaborate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#collaborate\" aria-label=\"collaborate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Collaborate</h2>\n<h5>Working with a team? These links are for you.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://c9.io\">Cloud9</a> - An awesome, zen way to work with others in the cloud.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com\">Gist</a> - Share code and text with others fast. Like a mini repository.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://scratchpad.io\">Scratchpad</a> - A simple, RTC tool for coding and previewing websites.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://redpen.io\">Red Pen</a> - Share your design and get feedback seamlessly.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.invoiceninja.com\">Invoice Ninja</a> - Open source invoicing platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"backends\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#backends\" aria-label=\"backends permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Backends</h2>\n<h5>Every awesome web app needs an awesome backend.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.firebase.com\">Firebase</a> - A real-time front-end database for your sites.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/\">DigitalOcean</a> - A cheap and quality VPS hosting company.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.heroku.com\">Heroku</a> - Cloud application platform; very easy to scale.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://auth0.com/\">Auth0</a> - Authentication, done for you.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hasura.io\">Hasura</a> - Platform to build and deploy app backends fast.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"testing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#testing\" aria-label=\"testing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Testing</h2>\n<h5>Before you launch, these are good tools to make sure your site is ready for stardom.</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.checkbot.io\">Checkbot</a> - Browser extension that tests your website follows 50+ SEO, speed and security best practices.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://placehold.it\">Placehold</a> - Generate custom placeholder images of any size.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.browserling.com/\">Browserling</a> - Cross-browser test your website.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://codepen.io\">CodePen</a> - A free web editor in your browser.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.woorank.com/\">WooRank</a> - A review tool for SEO elements, W3 validation, and numerous other variables. Free basic service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://yslow.org\">Yslow</a> - Tool for analyzing and finding fixes for multiple causes of slow site loading.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.hurl.it/\">Hurl.it</a> - Make HTTP requests in the browser.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://localtunnel.me\">Localtunnel</a> - Open localhost ports to the world.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.getpostman.com/\">Postman</a> - A tool to make HTTP requests, generate mock servers and make API documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"good-reads\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#good-reads\" aria-label=\"good reads permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Good Reads</h2>\n<h5>Need something to read in your spare time?</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.smashingmagazine.com\">Smashing Magazine</a> - A magazine for all things digital design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/\">CSS-Tricks</a> - Awesome blog on anything and everything related to CSS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://tympanus.net/codrops/\">Codrops</a> - Great collection of design techniques for modern web developmers and designers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.inserthtml.com\">Insert HTML</a> - A blog covering current and upcoming techniques and technologies for web developers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.1stwebdesigner.com/blog/\">1stWebDesign</a> - A good, simple blog on web development and design.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://alistapart.com\">A List Apart</a> - Guest bloggers and full books on topics from coding to business practices.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://goodui.org\">GoodUI</a> - It's definitely not bad.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.mentor.so/\">Mentor</a> - Get random advice from other designers and developers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"license\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/\"><img src=\"http://i.creativecommons.org/p/zero/1.0/88x31.png\" alt=\"CC0\"></a></p>\n<p>To the extent possible under law, <a href=\"http://noahbuscher.com\">Noah Buscher</a> has waived all copyright and related or neighboring rights to this work.</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img class=\"emoji-icon\" alt=\"emoji-heart\" data-icon=\"emoji-heart\" style=\"display: inline; margin: 0; margin-top: 1px; position: relative; top: 5px; width: 25px\" src=\"data:image/png;base64, \" title=\"emoji-heart\" /></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#inspire-awesome\">Inspire <img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#concept\">Concept</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#creation\">Creation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#tools\">Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#collaborate\">Collaborate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#backends\">Backends</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#testing\">Testing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#good-reads\">Good Reads</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#license\">License</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","headings":[{"id":"inspire-awesome","value":"Inspire Awesome","depth":1},{"id":"concept","value":"Concept","depth":2},{"id":"creation","value":"Creation","depth":2},{"id":"tools","value":"Tools","depth":2},{"id":"collaborate","value":"Collaborate","depth":2},{"id":"backends","value":"Backends","depth":2},{"id":"testing","value":"Testing","depth":2},{"id":"good-reads","value":"Good Reads","depth":2},{"id":"license","value":"License","depth":2}]},"awesomeList":{"repo":"noahbuscher/inspire","description":":bulb: Collection of web design & dev links","descriptionHTML":"<div>\n<g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"bulb\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4a1.png\">💡</g-emoji> Collection of web design &amp; dev links</div>"},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2021-06-27T23:15:28.185Z"},"previous":{"id":"59a915b8-40b6-53a0-b14a-7e0df830fd50","fields":{"repo":"petk/awesome-dojo","slug":"/petk/awesome-dojo/readme/"}},"next":{"id":"67d7ff47-55f7-5890-8931-e074cb05ec8e","fields":{"repo":"ember-community-russia/awesome-ember","slug":"/ember-community-russia/awesome-ember/readme/"}}},"pageContext":{"repo":"noahbuscher/inspire","id":"1c2f2879-bf38-5aa9-b20a-eab6ad0cec95","previousId":"59a915b8-40b6-53a0-b14a-7e0df830fd50","nextId":"67d7ff47-55f7-5890-8931-e074cb05ec8e"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","3289010534"]}